p style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#444444;margin:0 0 12px;\">목표</p>\n        <p style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#CCCCCC;margin:0;\">실무 적용<br>시간 절감<br>결과물 품질</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 중단 인용 -->\n    <div style=\"margin:64px 0;padding:40px 0;border-top:1px solid #222222;border-bottom:1px solid #222222;\">\n      <p style=\"font-size:clamp(18px,2.8vw,26px);font-weight:700;line-height:1.5;letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:#EFEFEF;margin:0;\">&ldquo;AI 강의가 넘쳐나는 시대. 코어 캠퍼스는 실제로 <em style=\"color:#FFFFFF;font-style:normal;\">작동하는 것</em>만 가르칩니다.&rdquo;</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- CTA + 부가 링크 -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:20px;\">\n      <a href=\"#curriculum\" style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;background:#FFFFFF;color:#111111;font-size:14px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:0.04em;padding:16px 32px;text-decoration:none;\">\n        <span>전체 커리큘럼 보기</span>\n        <span style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:300;\">→</span>\n      </a>\n      <div style=\"display:flex;gap:24px;\">\n        <a href=\"#review\" style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555555;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.06em;text-transform:uppercase;border-bottom:1px solid #333333;padding-bottom:2px;\">수강 후기</a>\n        <a href=\"#about\" style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555555;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.06em;text-transform:uppercase;border-bottom:1px solid #333333;padding-bottom:2px;\">소개</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>",
